{
  "stem": "9478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Russians chased out the Germans from our town, she was that time in the Czech army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because she was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was working in [NON-ENGLISH]-- [NON-ENGLISH] is in Russia, you know-- as a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then somehow, the chairman from the factory told her, you know then that the Gestapo is looking for you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She run away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as she run away, the Czech army came to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First, they chased out the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she knew that I'm alive someplace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she jumped in a truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she came to Korzec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she met a friend of mine what he was my place in Tashkent a few days ago.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Since then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the war was that time in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she ran away from the Germans to Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my friend, what he met my sister, this was already when Korzec was free from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was in the Czech army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she got permission to go to little town of Korzec and to find out if I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And accidentally, she met a friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he came from Tashkent going to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told her that I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Prague, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in Bytom when the war was still going on in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a phone call from my sister, because she married a major from the Czech army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she find out that I'm in Bytom, so she called us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then we grabbed a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A convoy of trucks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trucks-- a train, actually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we came to the station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the time it was at--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--at that time was a transport from the Romanian Jews going back from Auschwitz from Poland to Romania.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
